Third-party dependencies (not relicensable by this project):

  * poppler  — the PDF rendering engine, linked as a system library via
               pkg-config (GPL v2 for most files, with some GPL v2+ files).

NimblePDF links against poppler at build time rather than bundling its
source. The vendored xpdf 4.x tree (GPL v3, Glyph & Cog, LLC) was removed
during the poppler migration, so the combined distribution is now GPL v2 or
later — consistent with NimblePDF's own license and its BePDF heritage.

